# CODEOWNERS for ai-ops-managed projects.
# Distributed by `ai-ops setup-codeowners`. The `<owner>` placeholder is
# replaced with the project owner's GitHub username at install time.
#
# Routes ai-ops-related changes to the project owner so propagate-* PRs
# always land in the owner's review queue (per ADR 0011).

/.ai-ops/                       @<owner>
/.github/workflows/ai-ops*.yml  @<owner>
